cs.PL, cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.AI 

The paper discusses the implementation of smart contracts for financial derivatives, which involves programming languages and logic (cs.PL), machine learning and validation (cs.LG), security and cryptography (cs.CR), software engineering (cs.SE), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on formal methods for validation and assurance also suggests a strong connection to programming languages and logic.
